sellerAgent.name: Shelly Salas Your Home Sold Guaranteed

data.description: Your future home awaits! Step inside and discover an inviting living space with a thoughtfully designed layout. Throughout the home, you will find new carpeting and fresh paint. Your spacious living room features an elegant fireplace and arched entryways, adding a touch of elegance to the space. The kitchen boasts granite countertops, modern appliances, and a dining area with plenty of natural light streaming in through large windows. The master suite is a true retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom with a luxurious jetted tub and dual vanity. Step outside and be greeted by your own private outdoor oasis, complete with a covered patio area. Whether you're hosting a barbecue or unwinding after a long day, this spacious backyard offers endless possibilities! Additionally, the attached 2-car garage provides secure parking and extra storage space. Don't miss out on this exceptional opportunity. Schedule a showing today, and experience the comfort and beauty this home has to offer!
